<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top-left-radius: 10px;
            border-top-right-radius: 10px;
        }

        .order-details {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .order-details h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .order-details p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .order-details table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .order-details th,
        .order-details td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .order-details th {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .order-details td {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .order-details .total {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your CodeCanvas Order is Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-details">
            <p>Here's what you ordered:</p>
             <h2>Order Details:</h2>
            <p><strong>Order #: <%= order._id %></strong></p>
            <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= order.date %></p>

            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Item</th>
                    <th>Qty</th>
                    <th>Cost</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= order.name %></td>
                    <td>1</td>
                    <td><%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td class="total" colspan="2">Subtotal:</td>
                    <td class="total"><%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="total" colspan="2">Total:</td>
                    <td class="total"><%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@elearning.com">support@CodeCanvas.com</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2023 CodeCanvas. All rights reserved</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
